# AWS Account Creation
 
## What is AWS?
AWS (Amazon Web Services) is a cloud computing platform that provides servers, storage, networking, and many other services.
 
## Steps to Create AWS Account
1. Go to https://aws.amazon.com
2. Click "Create an AWS Account"
3. Enter email and password
4. Add billing details (card required)
5. Complete phone verification
6. Choose Free Tier plan
 
## Important Notes
- AWS works on pay-as-you-go model.
- Free tier is available for 12 months.
- Always stop/delete unused resources to avoid charges.
